item.title: You want me to put my hands where!?
item.author: Alisha Wong,
item.description: Last Wednesday, in typical gloomy and rainy weather, myself and eleven other Imperial girls from ICU Pole Dance trekked over to Hammersmith for the society’s very first Aerial ‘taster’ session. Aerial is a form of acrobatics, which is becoming increasingly popular as a fitness craze, and not just …
